{
  "video_id": "vKsxswK3RFg",
  "method": "api",
  "language": null,
  "duration_seconds": 2.4853956000879407,
  "entry_count": 181,
  "error": null,
  "entries": [
    {
      "time": "00:00",
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.18,
      "duration": 3.18,
      "text": "- [Instructor] A 50,000 kilogram plane"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:03",
      "start": 3.18,
      "end": 6.630000000000001,
      "duration": 3.45,
      "text": "is moving uncontrollably\nat one meter per second,"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:06",
      "start": 6.63,
      "end": 8.8,
      "duration": 2.17,
      "text": "and from the other side,"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:08",
      "start": 8.8,
      "end": 12.75,
      "duration": 3.95,
      "text": "a 2000 kilogram car is coming\nin, again, uncontrollably"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:12",
      "start": 12.75,
      "end": 14.79,
      "duration": 2.04,
      "text": "at 30 meters per second."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:14",
      "start": 14.79,
      "end": 16.66,
      "duration": 1.87,
      "text": "They are both on a collision course."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:16",
      "start": 16.66,
      "end": 19.1,
      "duration": 2.44,
      "text": "What's gonna happen?"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:19",
      "start": 19.1,
      "end": 23.330000000000002,
      "duration": 4.23,
      "text": "Well luckily, both Superman\nand Batman happen to be nearby,"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:23",
      "start": 23.33,
      "end": 25.799999999999997,
      "duration": 2.47,
      "text": "so they can go in and save the day."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:25",
      "start": 25.8,
      "end": 28.743000000000002,
      "duration": 2.943,
      "text": "But the question is who should stop what?"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:30",
      "start": 30.32,
      "end": 31.830000000000002,
      "duration": 1.51,
      "text": "I mean, it's no secret."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:31",
      "start": 31.83,
      "end": 34.97,
      "duration": 3.14,
      "text": "We all know Superman is\nstronger than Batman, right?"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:34",
      "start": 34.97,
      "end": 36.37,
      "duration": 1.4,
      "text": "No offense, Bats."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:36",
      "start": 36.37,
      "end": 38.589999999999996,
      "duration": 2.22,
      "text": "And so it'll make a lot of sense"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:38",
      "start": 38.59,
      "end": 41.720000000000006,
      "duration": 3.13,
      "text": "to assign the harder task to Superman."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:41",
      "start": 41.72,
      "end": 44.92,
      "duration": 3.2,
      "text": "And that's exactly what we need\nto figure out in this video."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:44",
      "start": 44.92,
      "end": 46.97,
      "duration": 2.05,
      "text": "We need to find out in which case"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:46",
      "start": 46.97,
      "end": 51.97,
      "duration": 5.0,
      "text": "it's gonna take more efforts\nto stop: the plane or the car."
    },
    {
      "time": "00:53",
      "start": 53.84,
      "end": 54.96,
      "duration": 1.12,
      "text": "So, what do you think?"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:54",
      "start": 54.96,
      "end": 56.93,
      "duration": 1.97,
      "text": "Which is harder to stop?"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:56",
      "start": 56.93,
      "end": 59.17,
      "duration": 2.24,
      "text": "Well, at first we might say,"
    },
    {
      "time": "00:59",
      "start": 59.17,
      "end": 62.550000000000004,
      "duration": 3.38,
      "text": "look, the plane is so much\nheavier compared to the car,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:02",
      "start": 62.55,
      "end": 65.09,
      "duration": 2.54,
      "text": "and so stopping the plane\nis going to be difficult."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:05",
      "start": 65.09,
      "end": 67.17,
      "duration": 2.08,
      "text": "I mean, you might know\nthe heavier something is,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:07",
      "start": 67.17,
      "end": 68.95,
      "duration": 1.78,
      "text": "more difficult it is to stop."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:08",
      "start": 68.95,
      "end": 70.9,
      "duration": 1.95,
      "text": "For example, if I threw\na bowling ball at you,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:10",
      "start": 70.9,
      "end": 72.45,
      "duration": 1.55,
      "text": "I won't do that, don't worry,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:12",
      "start": 72.45,
      "end": 74.47,
      "duration": 2.02,
      "text": "but if I did, it's harder to stop"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:14",
      "start": 74.47,
      "end": 77.42699999999999,
      "duration": 2.957,
      "text": "compared to if I threw a\nping pong ball at you, right?"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:17",
      "start": 77.427,
      "end": 80.07000000000001,
      "duration": 2.643,
      "text": "And so that way we can say\nbecause this is more massive,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:20",
      "start": 80.07,
      "end": 81.454,
      "duration": 1.384,
      "text": "it's harder to stop."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:21",
      "start": 81.454,
      "end": 84.55999999999999,
      "duration": 3.106,
      "text": "But on the other hand,\nif you look at the car,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:24",
      "start": 84.56,
      "end": 87.89,
      "duration": 3.33,
      "text": "that car is way faster than the airplane."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:27",
      "start": 87.89,
      "end": 89.56,
      "duration": 1.67,
      "text": "It's going at 30 meters per second,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:29",
      "start": 89.56,
      "end": 91.35000000000001,
      "duration": 1.79,
      "text": "and to give you some context,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:31",
      "start": 91.35,
      "end": 93.19999999999999,
      "duration": 1.85,
      "text": "if you convert that into\nkilometers per hour,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:33",
      "start": 93.2,
      "end": 95.60000000000001,
      "duration": 2.4,
      "text": "it's over 100 kilometers per hour."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:35",
      "start": 95.6,
      "end": 98.07,
      "duration": 2.47,
      "text": "That is pretty fast."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:38",
      "start": 98.07,
      "end": 100.75,
      "duration": 2.68,
      "text": "And you might know that if\nsomething is super fast,"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:40",
      "start": 100.75,
      "end": 103.32,
      "duration": 2.57,
      "text": "even then it's hard to stop, right?"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:43",
      "start": 103.32,
      "end": 105.88,
      "duration": 2.56,
      "text": "For example, that's why\nbullets are very hard to stop"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:45",
      "start": 105.88,
      "end": 109.193,
      "duration": 3.313,
      "text": "because they are light,\nbut they are pretty fast."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:50",
      "start": 110.41,
      "end": 112.86,
      "duration": 2.45,
      "text": "So, how do we decide?"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:52",
      "start": 112.86,
      "end": 117.39,
      "duration": 4.53,
      "text": "It seems as if the effort\nneeded to stop something"
    },
    {
      "time": "01:57",
      "start": 117.39,
      "end": 119.43,
      "duration": 2.04,
      "text": "depends on both of these things."
    },
    {
      "time": "01:59",
      "start": 119.43,
      "end": 121.81,
      "duration": 2.38,
      "text": "It depends on the mass of an object"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:01",
      "start": 121.81,
      "end": 124.83,
      "duration": 3.02,
      "text": "and it also depends on\nthe speed of that object."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:04",
      "start": 124.83,
      "end": 128.22,
      "duration": 3.39,
      "text": "And so, it turns out that in reality,"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:08",
      "start": 128.22,
      "end": 131.379,
      "duration": 3.159,
      "text": "the efforts needed depend on the product"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:11",
      "start": 131.379,
      "end": 134.35,
      "duration": 2.971,
      "text": "of the mass and the velocity."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:14",
      "start": 134.35,
      "end": 135.183,
      "duration": 0.833,
      "text": "All right?"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:15",
      "start": 135.183,
      "end": 139.23,
      "duration": 4.047,
      "text": "So, we come up with a new\nquantity for this purpose"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:19",
      "start": 139.23,
      "end": 142.774,
      "duration": 3.544,
      "text": "where we multiply the mass of the object"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:22",
      "start": 142.774,
      "end": 146.08,
      "duration": 3.306,
      "text": "with the velocity of the object."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:26",
      "start": 146.08,
      "end": 148.45000000000002,
      "duration": 2.37,
      "text": "It's this number that tells us"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:28",
      "start": 148.45,
      "end": 151.16,
      "duration": 2.71,
      "text": "how much efforts are\nneeded to stop that object."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:31",
      "start": 151.16,
      "end": 152.81,
      "duration": 1.65,
      "text": "And we give a name to this number."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:32",
      "start": 152.81,
      "end": 155.00300000000001,
      "duration": 2.193,
      "text": "We call this momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:36",
      "start": 156.41,
      "end": 159.26,
      "duration": 2.85,
      "text": "We call this as the momentum of the object"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:39",
      "start": 159.26,
      "end": 162.12,
      "duration": 2.86,
      "text": "and the symbol used for momentum is P"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:42",
      "start": 162.12,
      "end": 163.623,
      "duration": 1.503,
      "text": "because M is already taken."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:44",
      "start": 164.62,
      "end": 169.35,
      "duration": 4.73,
      "text": "And so, I like to think\nof momentum as a number"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:49",
      "start": 169.35,
      "end": 172.79999999999998,
      "duration": 3.45,
      "text": "that tells us how hard\nit is to stop something,"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:52",
      "start": 172.8,
      "end": 176.794,
      "duration": 3.994,
      "text": "which means more momentum,\nharder it is to stop an object."
    },
    {
      "time": "02:56",
      "start": 176.794,
      "end": 178.98000000000002,
      "duration": 2.186,
      "text": "Of course it turns out\nthere are other ways"
    },
    {
      "time": "02:58",
      "start": 178.98,
      "end": 181.20999999999998,
      "duration": 2.23,
      "text": "to think of momentum and\nwe will talk about them"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:01",
      "start": 181.21,
      "end": 184.58,
      "duration": 3.37,
      "text": "in other videos, but in this\nvideo we'll just stick to this."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:04",
      "start": 184.58,
      "end": 186.28,
      "duration": 1.7,
      "text": "Now, before we go ahead"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:06",
      "start": 186.28,
      "end": 188.36,
      "duration": 2.08,
      "text": "and calculate the momentum of these bodies"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:08",
      "start": 188.36,
      "end": 189.56,
      "duration": 1.2,
      "text": "and answer our question,"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:09",
      "start": 189.56,
      "end": 192.678,
      "duration": 3.118,
      "text": "let's get a little bit more\nfeeling for this formula."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:12",
      "start": 192.678,
      "end": 197.43,
      "duration": 4.752,
      "text": "This says that if the velocity\nof the object is zero,"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:17",
      "start": 197.43,
      "end": 199.255,
      "duration": 1.825,
      "text": "its momentum goes to zero."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:19",
      "start": 199.255,
      "end": 201.21,
      "duration": 1.955,
      "text": "Does that make sense?"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:21",
      "start": 201.21,
      "end": 202.87,
      "duration": 1.66,
      "text": "Well, it does, right?"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:22",
      "start": 202.87,
      "end": 204.5,
      "duration": 1.63,
      "text": "If something has zero velocity,"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:24",
      "start": 204.5,
      "end": 206.31,
      "duration": 1.81,
      "text": "it means it's not moving at all."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:26",
      "start": 206.31,
      "end": 208.24,
      "duration": 1.93,
      "text": "And if it's not moving at all,"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:28",
      "start": 208.24,
      "end": 210.88,
      "duration": 2.64,
      "text": "it doesn't take any efforts to stop,"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:30",
      "start": 210.88,
      "end": 214.92,
      "duration": 4.04,
      "text": "and so it makes sense to say\nits momentum is zero, okay?"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:34",
      "start": 214.92,
      "end": 217.61999999999998,
      "duration": 2.7,
      "text": "What about if its mass is zero?"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:37",
      "start": 217.62,
      "end": 219.583,
      "duration": 1.963,
      "text": "Even then, the momentum goes to zero."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:39",
      "start": 219.583,
      "end": 221.35999999999999,
      "duration": 1.777,
      "text": "Does that make sense?"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:41",
      "start": 221.36,
      "end": 222.193,
      "duration": 0.833,
      "text": "Well, yeah."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:42",
      "start": 222.193,
      "end": 223.92000000000002,
      "duration": 1.727,
      "text": "Imagine something which has zero mass."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:43",
      "start": 223.92,
      "end": 225.30499999999998,
      "duration": 1.385,
      "text": "Okay, that's hard to imagine."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:45",
      "start": 225.305,
      "end": 228.53,
      "duration": 3.225,
      "text": "Imagine something which\nis very, very light."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:48",
      "start": 228.53,
      "end": 231.08,
      "duration": 2.55,
      "text": "Say, very light compared\nto our body weight."
    },
    {
      "time": "03:51",
      "start": 231.08,
      "end": 233.14000000000001,
      "duration": 2.06,
      "text": "Imagine a mosquito, okay?"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:53",
      "start": 233.14,
      "end": 236.07,
      "duration": 2.93,
      "text": "Let's say I take a tiny mosquito,\nall mosquitoes are tiny,"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:56",
      "start": 236.07,
      "end": 239.81,
      "duration": 3.74,
      "text": "let's say I take a mosquito\nand I threw it at you, okay?"
    },
    {
      "time": "03:59",
      "start": 239.81,
      "end": 241.59,
      "duration": 1.78,
      "text": "Threw it at you at some speed."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:01",
      "start": 241.59,
      "end": 243.78,
      "duration": 2.19,
      "text": "How hard is it to stop that?"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:03",
      "start": 243.78,
      "end": 245.764,
      "duration": 1.984,
      "text": "Well, it's pretty easy, right?"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:05",
      "start": 245.764,
      "end": 248.14000000000001,
      "duration": 2.376,
      "text": "I mean, if I threw it\nat you, if it hits you,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:08",
      "start": 248.14,
      "end": 249.92999999999998,
      "duration": 1.79,
      "text": "you wouldn't even feel it, right?"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:09",
      "start": 249.93,
      "end": 251.48000000000002,
      "duration": 1.55,
      "text": "It's super easy to stop that."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:11",
      "start": 251.48,
      "end": 254.45,
      "duration": 2.97,
      "text": "And so, we could say that\nmomentum of a mosquito"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:14",
      "start": 254.45,
      "end": 256.39,
      "duration": 1.94,
      "text": "is pretty much zero."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:16",
      "start": 256.39,
      "end": 257.223,
      "duration": 0.833,
      "text": "Does that make sense?"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:17",
      "start": 257.223,
      "end": 259.71000000000004,
      "duration": 2.487,
      "text": "So if something has very small mass,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:19",
      "start": 259.71,
      "end": 261.83,
      "duration": 2.12,
      "text": "it has very small momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:21",
      "start": 261.83,
      "end": 263.88,
      "duration": 2.05,
      "text": "That's what it means over here."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:23",
      "start": 263.88,
      "end": 266.34,
      "duration": 2.46,
      "text": "On the other hand, imagine\nsomething which has both"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:26",
      "start": 266.34,
      "end": 269.45,
      "duration": 3.11,
      "text": "very high mass and high velocity."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:29",
      "start": 269.45,
      "end": 272.84,
      "duration": 3.39,
      "text": "Now, it has super high momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:32",
      "start": 272.84,
      "end": 273.81,
      "duration": 0.97,
      "text": "Does that make sense?"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:33",
      "start": 273.81,
      "end": 275.089,
      "duration": 1.279,
      "text": "Well, yeah."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:35",
      "start": 275.089,
      "end": 279.129,
      "duration": 4.04,
      "text": "I mean, imagine a freight\ntrain, which is very heavy,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:39",
      "start": 279.129,
      "end": 282.58000000000004,
      "duration": 3.451,
      "text": "and let's say it's going\nat 100 kilometers per hour."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:42",
      "start": 282.58,
      "end": 283.82,
      "duration": 1.24,
      "text": "Ooo."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:43",
      "start": 283.82,
      "end": 285.89,
      "duration": 2.07,
      "text": "Can you imagine trying to stop that?"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:45",
      "start": 285.89,
      "end": 288.78,
      "duration": 2.89,
      "text": "That is gonna be super hard to stop,"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:48",
      "start": 288.78,
      "end": 292.363,
      "duration": 3.583,
      "text": "so it makes sense to say it\nhas very, very high momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:53",
      "start": 293.77,
      "end": 295.24,
      "duration": 1.47,
      "text": "All right, another quick thing we'll do"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:55",
      "start": 295.24,
      "end": 296.81,
      "duration": 1.57,
      "text": "is figure out its units."
    },
    {
      "time": "04:56",
      "start": 296.81,
      "end": 298.14,
      "duration": 1.33,
      "text": "In fact, can you try this?"
    },
    {
      "time": "04:58",
      "start": 298.14,
      "end": 302.09999999999997,
      "duration": 3.96,
      "text": "Can you think about what the\nunits of momentum is gonna be?"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:02",
      "start": 302.1,
      "end": 303.1,
      "duration": 1.0,
      "text": "Just give it a shot."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:04",
      "start": 304.78,
      "end": 306.36999999999995,
      "duration": 1.59,
      "text": "Okay, let's see."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:06",
      "start": 306.37,
      "end": 308.693,
      "duration": 2.323,
      "text": "Mass has a unit of kilograms."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:10",
      "start": 310.0,
      "end": 312.03,
      "duration": 2.03,
      "text": "Velocity has a unit of meters per second,"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:12",
      "start": 312.03,
      "end": 313.10999999999996,
      "duration": 1.08,
      "text": "so when you're multiplying that,"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:13",
      "start": 313.11,
      "end": 314.28000000000003,
      "duration": 1.17,
      "text": "even the units get multiplied."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:14",
      "start": 314.28,
      "end": 317.38,
      "duration": 3.1,
      "text": "So it's gonna be kilograms\nmeters per second."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:17",
      "start": 317.38,
      "end": 318.943,
      "duration": 1.563,
      "text": "That's the unit of momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:19",
      "start": 319.82,
      "end": 321.8,
      "duration": 1.98,
      "text": "All right, and now comes the moment"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:21",
      "start": 321.8,
      "end": 323.26,
      "duration": 1.46,
      "text": "that we've been waiting for."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:23",
      "start": 323.26,
      "end": 326.14,
      "duration": 2.88,
      "text": "We can go ahead and calculate the momenta"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:26",
      "start": 326.14,
      "end": 327.91999999999996,
      "duration": 1.78,
      "text": "of both of these objects."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:27",
      "start": 327.92,
      "end": 332.63,
      "duration": 4.71,
      "text": "And by the way, momentum is\nsingular, momenta is plural."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:32",
      "start": 332.63,
      "end": 335.44,
      "duration": 2.81,
      "text": "So anyways, we can calculate\nthe momenta of both of them"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:35",
      "start": 335.44,
      "end": 337.64,
      "duration": 2.2,
      "text": "and figure out which one is higher."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:37",
      "start": 337.64,
      "end": 341.19,
      "duration": 3.55,
      "text": "Whichever is higher, that\nwould be harder to stop."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:41",
      "start": 341.19,
      "end": 343.66,
      "duration": 2.47,
      "text": "Now, I know you are super,\nsuper excited to do this,"
    },
    {
      "time": "05:43",
      "start": 343.66,
      "end": 345.56,
      "duration": 1.9,
      "text": "so why not give it a shot first."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:45",
      "start": 345.56,
      "end": 349.583,
      "duration": 4.023,
      "text": "Pause the video, go ahead\nand calculate the momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:52",
      "start": 352.4,
      "end": 354.28,
      "duration": 1.88,
      "text": "All right, let's do this."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:54",
      "start": 354.28,
      "end": 357.34299999999996,
      "duration": 3.063,
      "text": "So, let's first do the\nmomentum of the airplane."
    },
    {
      "time": "05:58",
      "start": 358.61,
      "end": 361.42,
      "duration": 2.81,
      "text": "I'm gonna call P-A, A for airplane."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:01",
      "start": 361.42,
      "end": 363.69,
      "duration": 2.27,
      "text": "That's going to be the\nmass of the airplane,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:03",
      "start": 363.69,
      "end": 366.46999999999997,
      "duration": 2.78,
      "text": "which is 50,000 kilograms."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:06",
      "start": 366.47,
      "end": 371.47,
      "duration": 5.0,
      "text": "So, 50,000 kilograms times\nthe velocity of the airplane."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:13",
      "start": 373.09,
      "end": 375.09,
      "duration": 2.0,
      "text": "That's going to be one meter per second."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:16",
      "start": 376.0,
      "end": 377.43,
      "duration": 1.43,
      "text": "And how much is that?"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:17",
      "start": 377.43,
      "end": 381.36,
      "duration": 3.93,
      "text": "Well that is 50,000 times\none, that's just 50,000."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:21",
      "start": 381.36,
      "end": 383.04,
      "duration": 1.68,
      "text": "50,000."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:23",
      "start": 383.04,
      "end": 384.05,
      "duration": 1.01,
      "text": "And the units are,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:24",
      "start": 384.05,
      "end": 385.90000000000003,
      "duration": 1.85,
      "text": "notice I don't have to remember the units."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:25",
      "start": 385.9,
      "end": 386.94,
      "duration": 1.04,
      "text": "I'll just look at this"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:26",
      "start": 386.94,
      "end": 388.55,
      "duration": 1.61,
      "text": "and I can multiply the units here itself."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:28",
      "start": 388.55,
      "end": 392.88300000000004,
      "duration": 4.333,
      "text": "So, the units are going to be\nkilogram meters per second."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:34",
      "start": 394.41,
      "end": 396.56,
      "duration": 2.15,
      "text": "Okay, let's do the car now."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:36",
      "start": 396.56,
      "end": 400.75,
      "duration": 4.19,
      "text": "The momentum of the car,\nwhich we'll P-C, C for car,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:40",
      "start": 400.75,
      "end": 402.83,
      "duration": 2.08,
      "text": "that's going to be mass of the car,"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:42",
      "start": 402.83,
      "end": 405.77,
      "duration": 2.94,
      "text": "which is just 2000 kilograms"
    },
    {
      "time": "06:46",
      "start": 406.76,
      "end": 409.53,
      "duration": 2.77,
      "text": "times the velocity of that car."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:49",
      "start": 409.53,
      "end": 412.10299999999995,
      "duration": 2.573,
      "text": "That's gonna be 30 meters per second."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:53",
      "start": 413.27,
      "end": 416.88,
      "duration": 3.61,
      "text": "And that will be, let's\nsee how much that is."
    },
    {
      "time": "06:56",
      "start": 416.88,
      "end": 421.06,
      "duration": 4.18,
      "text": "Two times three is six,\none two three four,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:01",
      "start": 421.06,
      "end": 426.06,
      "duration": 5.0,
      "text": "60,000 kilogram meters per second."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:07",
      "start": 427.17,
      "end": 430.47,
      "duration": 3.3,
      "text": "So, which one is higher?"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:10",
      "start": 430.47,
      "end": 432.24,
      "duration": 1.77,
      "text": "Well, it's the car."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:12",
      "start": 432.24,
      "end": 435.29,
      "duration": 3.05,
      "text": "The car turns out to\nhave a higher momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:15",
      "start": 435.29,
      "end": 440.04,
      "duration": 4.75,
      "text": "That means it'll take more\nefforts to stop that car."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:20",
      "start": 440.04,
      "end": 441.91,
      "duration": 1.87,
      "text": "So even though the car was lighter,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:21",
      "start": 441.91,
      "end": 443.5,
      "duration": 1.59,
      "text": "much lighter compared to the airplane,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:23",
      "start": 443.5,
      "end": 445.95,
      "duration": 2.45,
      "text": "it is going so much faster"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:25",
      "start": 445.95,
      "end": 448.21999999999997,
      "duration": 2.27,
      "text": "that it turns out it takes\nmore efforts to stop it."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:28",
      "start": 448.22,
      "end": 449.47,
      "duration": 1.25,
      "text": "It has a higher momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:30",
      "start": 450.48,
      "end": 452.12,
      "duration": 1.64,
      "text": "And so, now we know what to do."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:32",
      "start": 452.12,
      "end": 453.69,
      "duration": 1.57,
      "text": "Since the car is the one\nthat's harder to stop,"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:33",
      "start": 453.69,
      "end": 456.13,
      "duration": 2.44,
      "text": "we can assign that to Superman."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:36",
      "start": 456.13,
      "end": 459.553,
      "duration": 3.423,
      "text": "Batman gets the airplane\nand our day gets saved."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:40",
      "start": 460.42,
      "end": 462.51,
      "duration": 2.09,
      "text": "And so, what did we learn in this video?"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:42",
      "start": 462.51,
      "end": 465.21999999999997,
      "duration": 2.71,
      "text": "We learned of a new\nquantity called momentum."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:45",
      "start": 465.22,
      "end": 466.91,
      "duration": 1.69,
      "text": "We can think of it as a number"
    },
    {
      "time": "07:46",
      "start": 466.91,
      "end": 469.31,
      "duration": 2.4,
      "text": "which tells us how hard\nit is to stop something."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:49",
      "start": 469.31,
      "end": 472.03000000000003,
      "duration": 2.72,
      "text": "More momentum, harder it is to stop."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:52",
      "start": 472.03,
      "end": 474.11999999999995,
      "duration": 2.09,
      "text": "And we also learned how to calculate it."
    },
    {
      "time": "07:54",
      "start": 474.12,
      "end": 477.793,
      "duration": 3.673,
      "text": "We calculate it as a product\nof mass and velocity."
    }
  ]
}